title: Daisy Bo Peep
description: Daisy Duck has lost Bo Peep's sheep and doesn't know where to find them!

title: A Surprise for Minnie
description: Mickey needs help to make and deliver a Valentine's Day card to Minnie.

title: Goofy's Bird
description: Goofy finds a lost baby bird and Mickey helps him bring it back home to his mommy in the forest.

title: Donald's Big Balloon Race
description: Mickey helps Donald fly in the Big Balloon Race so he can win a Big Blue Ribbon.

title: Mickey Goes Fishing
description: Goofy drops off his kitten, Mr. Pettibone, at the Clubhouse for the day.

title: Donald and the Beanstalk
description: Donald trades his favorite pet, Boo Boo Chicken, for five magic beans.

title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse - Minnie's Birthday
description: Mickey and friends need help throwing a surprise party for Minnie.

title: Donald and the Frog Prince
description: Donald gets turned into a frog when he drinks Professor Von Drake's new potion.

title: Goofy's Mars
description: When Goofy crash lands on Mars, it's up to Mickey and friends to save him.

title: Mickey-Go-Seek
description: During a game of Hide-and-Seek, Mickey has to find Donald, who's never been found before.

title: Daisy's Dance
description: Daisy wants to enter the Talent Show but suddenly comes down with a bad case of stage fright.

title: Pluto's Ball
description: Mickey and the gang get Pluto's favorite Super-Duper Bouncy Ball back when it bounces away.

title: Mickey's Treasure Hunt
description: Mickey finds a note with riddle-like directions to a treasure hidden somewhere in the Clubhouse.

title: Pluto's Puppy-Sitting Adventure
description: Clarabelle Cow asks Mickey and Pluto to puppy-sit her new pooch, Ginger.

title: Daisy in the Sky
description: On Balloon Day, Daisy grabs a large batch of balloons and gets literally carried away.

title: Pluto's Best
description: Pluto plays a series of games with Pete's dog Butch to see who'll win the big gold dog-bone trophy.

title: Mickey's Treat
description: The Sensational Six enlist our help in getting to the Trick-or-Treat Tower for the Halloween Party.

title: Minnie Red Riding Hood
description: Mickey and Minnie set out to take some Feel Better Soup to a cold-stricken Goofy.

title: Sleeping Minnie
description: Minnie accidentally picks a Sleeping Rose from the Clubhouse Garden and falls into a 100-year sleep.

title: Mickey Saves Santa
description: The gang is ready to celebrate Christmas Eve when Santa's sleigh breaks down!

title: Goofy the Great
description: Goofy's getting ready to perform in his magic show when suddenly all his tricks fall apart!

title: Mickey's Color Adventure
description: The Rainbow Color Machine is running low and colors are draining out of the Clubhouse!

title: Goofy's Petting Zoo
description: The animals at the petting zoo escape so Mickey and Goofy set out to round them up.

title: Donald's Lost Lion
description: Donald loses his favorite toy Sparky, a roaring, stuffed lion.

title: Doctor Daisy, MD
description: When Daisy helps make Goofy feel better, the word spreads and she soon has a line of "patients."

title: Donald's Hiccups
description: Donald gets the hiccups and spreads them to the rest of the Sensational Six!

title: Fancy Dancin' Goofy
description: Goofy's going to the Dance with Clarabelle, but he needs help learning how to "fancy dance!"

title: Goofy the Homemaker
description: Goofy decides to build a birdy-house for a baby red bird and his mommy.

title: Mickey's Handy Helpers
description: When the Handy Helpers go limp, Mickey finds the machine that makes the clubhouse work is broken.

title: Goofy Baby
description: Professor Von Drake has invented a time machine and Goofy is his first volunteer.

title: Minnie's Picnic
description: Minnie's having a picnic to celebrate the new Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Picnic Grounds!

title: Goofy in Training
description: Goofy needs help learning the difference between left and right, and up, down and over.

title: Mickey's Big Band Concert
description: The Polka Band is planning to provide musical accompaniment for a dance performance.

title: Goofy's Hat
description: When Goofy loses his hat, he doesn't feel goofy anymore, so Mickey and friends must find it!

title: Donald's Special Delivery
description: Donald gets upset when all of his friends get mail, but he doesn't get any.

title: Daisy's Pet Project
description: There's going to be a Pet Parade at the Clubhouse, but Daisy doesn't have her own pet!

title: Clarabelle's Clubhouse Carnival
description: Mickey and his friends put on a carnival to help Clarabelle collect pieces of corn for her chickens.

title: Mickey and Minnie's Jungle Safari
description: Minnie is determined to snap a photo of the rare Hula Hibiscus that only blooms once a year.

title: Mickey's Art Show
description: Mickey's putting on an arts and crafts show and everyone busily works on their art.

title: Mickey's Camp Out
description: Mickey and his friends set out to earn Clubhouse Camp Out Badges.

title: Mickey's Round Up
description: A box of wild numbers with minds of their own run loose in the Clubhouse!

title: Mickey's Big Job
description: When the Giant decides to visit his Mama, he asks Mickey and his friends to house-sit his farm.

title: Pluto's Bubble Bath
description: When Pluto's bubble bath gets out of hand, Mickey and Pluto each get stuck in a Giant Bubble!

title: Mickey's Silly Problem
description: When the Clubhouse's Silly Switch gets stuck on silly, everything turns silly.

title: Mickey's Thanks a Bunch Day
description: It's Thanks A Bunch Day, the day that Mickey and friends give thanks.

title: Secret Spy Daisy
description: Sneaky Pete tries to get Clarabelle's special recipe for Monster Raisin Cookies.

title: Pluto to the Rescue!
description: Donald and Goofy love making snow sculptures on the top of Mistletoe Mountain!

title: Sir Goofs-a-lot
description: Goofy finally gets his chance to be a knight when Queen Clarabelle sends Goofy on a quest.

title: Minnie's Mystery
description: When things in the Clubhouse are missing, everyone sets out to find out how to solve the mystery.

title: Mickey's Comet
description: When Professor Von Drake sets up a telescope, he forgets to tell everyone where he's going to be!

title: Clarabelle's Clubhouse Mooooo-sical
description: Everyone's excited today because Clarabelle is putting on a musical about Nursery Rhymes.

title: Minnie's Rainbow
description: When a rainbow appears over the Clubhouse, Mickey and friends set out to find its end.

title: Space Captain Donald
description: When Pluto's bouncy ball bounces all the way into space, Mickey and friends take a trip to the Moon.

title: The Friendship Team
description: Daisy and Minnie team up to find the stolen hats for Clubhouse Friendship Day.

title: Mickey's Message From Mars
description: When the Professor finds a mysterious pattern of lights flashing, the gang flies up to space!

title: Pete's Beach Blanket Luau
description: It's the hottest day of the year and Pete decides to put on a Luau down at the lake to cool off.

title: Minnie's Bee Story
description: Buzzby the Bee has a problem: A strong wind blew him away from his sunflower in Mickey Park!

title: Pluto's Playmate
description: Salty the seal is going to be the star of Mickey's Circus, but the seal doesn't know any tricks.

title: Donald's Ducks
description: Ten ducks need help getting to a beach for the winter and Donald eagerly volunteers to help.

title: Goofy's Coconutty Monkey
description: Goofy's good friend Coco the Monkey is planning to have a Coconutty Milk Party for everyone.

title: Mickey and the Enchanted Egg
description: Mickey finds an egg which soon hatches a Baby Dinosaur.

title: Goofy Goes Goofy
description: Goofy accidentally gets soaked with the Professor's experimental goo and splits into twelve Goofys!

title: Goofy's Super Wish
description: Goofy wishes he could be a super-hero so that he can help out his friends.

title: Mickey's Big Surprise
description: Mickey has a big surprise for everyone if they can solve his five Fun Puzzles.

title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse - Choo-Choo Express
description: Mickey and his friends put together a Choo-Choo train and use it to help Professor Von Drake.

title: Goofy's Goofbot
description: Today is Build-Your-Own-Toy Day, and Goofy needs help building his toy robot in time for the Fair.

title: Mickey's Springtime Surprise
description: It's the first day of spring and Mickey and friends celebrate by looking for decorated eggs.

title: Super Goof's Super Puzzle
description: The super-"villain" Puzzler-Pete challenges Goofy and his friends to solve his Super-Duper Puzzle.

title: Donald of the Desert
description: Mickey and his friends meet Genie-Pete who grants Donald a single wish!

title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse - Happy Birthday, Toodles
description: It's Toodles' birthday and the Sensational Six set out to celebrate with a surprise party.

title: Goofy's Magical Mix-Up
description: When Goofy accidentally causes things to disappear, he needs everyone's help finding all of it.

title: Pluto's Dinosaur Romp
description: When Pluto's bouncy-ball bounces into the Time Machine, it bounces out again followed by a dinosaur!

title: Minnie's Pajama Party
description: Minnie sets up a fun Pajama Party sleepover. But when it's time to go to sleep, nobody's sleepy yet!

title: Road Rally
description: For the big Road Rally, Mickey and friends zoom around the Clubhouse in a race where everyone wins!

title: Donald the Genie
description: The magical Genie of the Desert arrives and fixes Donald's fishing rod with a magical zap.

title: Mickey's Mousekersize!
description: Mickey and his friends show Pete that exercising can be fun!

title: Mickey's Little Parade
description: The Clubhouse's smallest friends are all set to march in the Little Parade.

title: Minnie's Mouseke-Calendar
description: After a wind blows away the pages from Minnie's calendar, she needs help finding the missing pages.

title: Pluto Lends a Paw
description: When Minnie's cat Figaro wanders off, Pluto the Rescue Dog takes charge and finds the missing pet.

title: Minnie's Bow-tique
description: It's the grand opening of Minnie's Bow-tique, a store packed with all kinds of bows and bowties!

title: Minnie's Masquerade
description: The Clubhouse pals are excited to dress up in their favorite costumes for Minnie's Masquerade Ball.

title: Goofy's Giant Adventure
description: Sir Goofs-a-lot goes on a fairytale quest to bring back the cure for Willy the Giant's tummy ache.

title: Donald's Clubhouse
description: When Mickey goes to help Clarabelle at the Moo Mart, Donald takes care of the Clubhouse.

title: Mickey's Show and Tell
description: Mickey's having Show and Tell with Shapes and everybody's bringing their favorite shapes.

title: Mickey's Fishy Story
description: When Daisy wants to find a friend for her fish, the gang helps her find other fish in the Jungle.

title: The Go-Getters
description: The Go-Getters must find some Giant Baby Chicks.

title: Goofy's Gone
description: The Go-Getters lead us in an exciting game of hide and seek.

title: Goofy Babysitter
description: Von Drake's Time Machine accidentally turns Mickey, Minnie, Donald, Daisy and Pluto into toddlers!

title: Space Adventure
description: Mickey and the gang rocket into space to search for Treasure.

title: Daisy's Grasshopper
description: Daisy Duck brings a new friend to the Clubhouse, Wilbur the Grasshopper!

title: Pluto's Tale
description: Prince Pluto saves the Princess from Wizard Pete.

title: Goofy's Thinking Cap
description: Goofy uses a special Thinking Cap to solve Clarabelle Cow's Scavenger Hunt!

title: Minnie and Daisy's Flower Shower
description: Minnie and Daisy board the Glove Balloon to make rain clouds so they can water their gardens.

title: Prince Pete's Catnap
description: Prince Pete is cranky - he cannot fall asleep! It's up to our Clubhouse pals to help him take a nap.

title: Aye, Aye Captain Mickey
description: The Sensational Six board Professor Von Drake's new submarine to recover Mickey's Lucky Coin.

title: Donald Hatches An Egg
description: Donald has to take care of a lost egg while all the Clubhouse friends look for the egg's family.

title: The Golden Boo-Boo
description: Daisy O'Dare loves Adventure Day, and we're with her in search of the Golden Boo-Boo!

title: Mickey and Donald Have a Farm
description: Mickey and his pals set out to rescue all of the missing animals from the Clubhouse Farm!

title: Quest for the Crystal Mickey!
description: An extraordinary hero shows up to save the day after a legendary statue is taken from the Clubhouse.

title: Daisy's Pony Tale
description: Professor Von Drake's new invention accidentally makes Daisy's hair grow super long!

title: Mickey's Farm Fun-Fair!
description: Mickey hosts a farm fun-fair with an Egg-in-the-Spoon Race, a Bake-Off, and more!

title: The Wizard of Dizz!
description: Minnie and Pluto get swept up and find themselves in a strange and wonderful world.

title: Super Adventure!
description: Super Mickey and the Clubhouse Heroes must work as a team to save the Clubhouse from Megamort!

title: Mickey's Mystery!
description: Kansas City Mickey returns to lead the Clubhouse team on another adventure.

title: Minnie's Pet Salon
description: It's time for Pluto's All-Star Pet Show at Minnie's Pet Salon.

title: Minnie-rella
description: Minnie-rella can't wait for Prince Mickey's Grand Ball, but the magical spell from her Fairy Godmother is going to be broken at midnight!

title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse - Mickey's Clubhouse Rocks
description: Mickey and Minnie are working on a rockin' song for a Clubhouse Battle of the Bands.

title: Donald Jr.
description: Donald teaches Donald Jr. the steps to a special song and dance on "Show Your Special Talent Day."

title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse - Sea Captain Mickey
description: Mickey and the gang hop into the Clubhouse Submarine and set out to find the "Big Something".

title: Mickey's Pirate Adventure
description: The Clubhousers are spending the day at the beach, when Pegleg Pete sails to shore with a note from Goofy's long lost Grandpappy, Captain Goof-Beard.

title: Mickey's Happy Mousekeday
description: It's Mickey's birthday and for his birthday present, his pals have organized fun things for the big Mousekeday. But when problems occur, Mickey takes time out to help his pals.

title: Minnie's Winter Bow Show
description: While Minnie is preparing for her Winter Bow Show, she and her nieces, Millie and Melody, accidentally go off on a wild winter wonderland adventure to the Clubhouse North Pole!

title: Around the Clubhouse World
description: Professor Von Drake gives Mickey a special Clubhouse Passport that has to get stamped at four different "farrrrr-away" locations in order to receive a super-duper, surprise prize!

title: Mickey's Mousekeball
description: Professor Von Drake introduces the Clubhouse pals to a high-tech new game, Floatin' Fun-Time Mousekeball!  But when the ball escapes, the game takes to the skies!

title: Donald's Brand New Clubhouse
description: When Donald feels like everybody's getting in his way in Mickey's Clubhouse, he decides that he wants his own. So, Mickey and pals help Donald build a clubhouse just for himself.

title: Mickey's Mousekedoer Adventure
description: When the Mousekedoer malfunctions, Professor Von Drake comes to a realization. The only way to make the repairs is to shrink the Clubhousers and send them inside the machine.

title: Mickey's Monster Musical
description: When the toon car breaks down, Mickey, Minnie, and Pluto head over to an old castle to see if anyone can help them. As they enter the castle, Mickey and Minnie meet COUNT MIKULA!

title: Pop Star Minnie
description: When Minnie is invited to sing at the top of Mistletoe Mountain, Mickey gathers all their friends to be the back-up band. But, soon they realize all the instruments are missing!

title: Chef Goofy on the Go!
description: Word is out that Goofy's got a lunch truck and all the Clubhouse pals phone in their orders! Nothing will stop Chef Goofy from making his deeelicious deliveries!

title: Oh, Toodles!
description: Professor Von Drake is working on a surprise invention when he discovers that he is missing four of his tools. Toodles helps Mickey find them with Mouseketools and a checklist.

title: Mickey's Sport-Y-Thon
description: Put on your sneakers, sports fans! Today is the first ever Mickey Mouse Sport-a-thon! It’s an action-filled sports tournament that draws athletes from around the Clubhouse.

title: Martian Minnie's Tea Party
description: Minnie's on her way to Mars on an urgent mission! Her assignment? Help her outer space twin, Martian Minnie, host a tea party for our Clubhouse friends throughout the galaxy!

title: A Goofy Fairy Tale
description: It’s bedtime at the Clubhouse and everyone’s ready for their favorite bedtime stories! Unfortunately, Goofy’s magic trick makes all the stories disappear from the Clubhouse books!
